'''Allan Bird''' (born 1953) is a university professor and holds the Darla and Frederick Brodsky Trustee Professor in Global Business at [[Northeastern University]]. He is an author of numerous scholarly works in the areas of [[Global Leadership|global leadership]] and international [[human resource management]] that, according to [[Google Scholar]] has 4651 citations bringing his h-index to 33 and his ¡10-index to 56.<ref>https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=ajHipWIAAAAJ&hl=en&oi=ao</ref>

